ittham-aṅganā:-	thus the women
cittayoni-janitāt-	the Cupid's caused
anugrahāt	blessings
baddha-rāga-vivaśā:-	bonding into attachment and so helpless
tvayi prabho	towards Thee O Lord!
nityam-āpu:-	always attained
